, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday's A final\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"a sun-kissed Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doyle and Lynch hadbreezed through their heat and semi-finalbut the duo from Banbridge, Co Down and Clonmel, Co Tipperary respectively had to work for their rewards in the final.\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Banbridge\", \"score\": 0.9999999995420694, \"rank\": 4.5814490510499705e-10, \"text\": \"Banbridge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Banbridge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Banbridge\"}, {\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Co Down\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Down\"}, {\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tipperary_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9999999677611419, \"rank\": 3.22387856508882e-08, \"text\": \"Tipperary\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tipperary_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tipperary_GAA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Doyle\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"Lynch\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"their heat\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"the duo\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"their rewards\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1576}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the USA lurking with intent in the hope of nabbing the last medal on offer, Ireland's pair had to show resilience in the final stages of the race toclaim the third spot on the podium and a first heavyweight rowing medal for Ireland at an Olympics.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9814668080619762, \"rank\": 0.018873912040022697, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999990700417, \"rank\": 9.297394779568563e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999990700417, \"rank\": 9.297394779568563e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"intent\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the hope\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1636}, {\"ngram\": \"the last medal\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"offer\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"the final stages\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"the race toclaim\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"the third spot\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"a first heavyweight rowing medal\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's nice to write that into the history books,\\\" an e